## Transitions & Motion

### Standard Timing
```css
:root {
  --transition-fast: 0.15s ease;      /* Quick feedback */
  --transition-normal: 0.2s ease;     /* Standard interactions */
  --transition-slow: 0.3s ease;       /* Layout changes */
  --transition-enter: 0.2s ease-out;  /* Entrance animations */
  --transition-exit: 0.15s ease-in;   /* Exit animations */
}
```

### Motion Preferences
```css
/* Respect user motion preferences */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  * {
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
  }
}
```

### Common Transition Patterns
```css
/* Smooth hover effects */
.interactive {
  transition: all var(--transition-normal);
}

/* Transform-based animations (performant) */
.hover-lift:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  transition: transform var(--transition-normal);
}

/* Opacity fades */
.fade-in {
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeIn var(--transition-enter) forwards;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  to { opacity: 1; }
}
```

## Accessibility Foundations

### Focus Management
```css
/* Consistent focus styles */
.focusable:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--primary);
  outline-offset: 2px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
}

/* Remove focus for mouse users */
.focusable:focus:not(:focus-visible) {
  outline: none;
}
```

### Color Contrast
All color combinations must meet **WCAG AA standards**:
- Normal text: 4.5:1 contrast ratio minimum
- Large text: 3:1 contrast ratio minimum
- UI components: 3:1 contrast ratio minimum

