## Performance Foundations

### Efficient Animations
```css
/* Use transform and opacity for smooth animations */
.performant-animation {
  will-change: transform, opacity;
  transform: translateZ(0); /* Force hardware acceleration */
}

/* Avoid animating expensive properties */
.avoid {
  /* Don't animate: width, height, background-color, border-width */
}
```

### Loading States
```css
.loading {
  position: relative;
  pointer-events: none;
  opacity: 0.6;
}

.loading::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  margin: -10px 0 0 -10px;
  border: 2px solid var(--gray-300);
  border-top-color: var(--primary);
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes spin {
  to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}
```

## Implementation Guidelines

### CSS Organization
```css
/* Foundation styles should be imported first */
@import 'foundations/tokens.css';
@import 'foundations/reset.css';
@import 'foundations/typography.css';
@import 'foundations/layout.css';

/* Then component styles */
@import 'components/button.css';
@import 'components/card.css';
```

### Token Usage
- **Always use CSS custom properties** instead of hardcoded values
- **Apply tokens consistently** across components
- **Document deviations** when foundation tokens don't meet specific needs
- **Test at multiple viewport sizes** to ensure responsive behavior

